  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/5a9fafd067a82e04467b702542685aa0.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=181 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ FEATURES ~ </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 8-12 hours of gameplay.<br></li><li> Collect souls for the king of demons, Yaphett.<br></li><li> Feed those souls into the volcano to gain power.<br></li><li> Sling spells and magical abilities, strategize your upgrades, and survive explosive confrontations.<br></li><li> Experience unforgettable NPCs painted with passion.<br></li><li> Brave relentless waves of adversaries in roguelike flavored endless challenge zones.<br></li><li> Collect Battlecrab TM cards! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/7137920932d9fd5318c561621658ebad.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ BONUS FEATURES ~ </h2><i> ~ Based on the comic book, Pluto's Island ~ </i><br><br><i> ~ Exclusive soundtrack from Ark Patrol for maximum vibes ~ </i><br><br><i> ~ I tried my best to make it pretty good ~ </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/bc81a9c10895eed05b3a34d40368d710.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/5a9fafd067a82e04467b702542685aa0.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=181 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ FEATURES ~ </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 8-12 hours of gameplay.<br></li><li> Collect souls for the king of demons, Yaphett.<br></li><li> Feed those souls into the volcano to gain power.<br></li><li> Sling spells and magical abilities, strategize your upgrades, and survive explosive confrontations.<br></li><li> Experience unforgettable NPCs painted with passion.<br></li><li> Brave relentless waves of adversaries in roguelike flavored endless challenge zones.<br></li><li> Collect Battlecrab TM cards! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/7137920932d9fd5318c561621658ebad.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ~ BONUS FEATURES ~ </h2><i> ~ Based on the comic book, Pluto's Island ~ </i><br><br><i> ~ Exclusive soundtrack from Ark Patrol for maximum vibes ~ </i><br><br><i> ~ I tried my best to make it pretty good ~ </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881290/extras/bc81a9c10895eed05b3a34d40368d710.avif?t=1701266420\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
